<body>
	<main>
		<div class="homeHeaderBackground position-relative overflow-hidden p-3 p-md-5 m-md-3 text-center">
			<div class="col-md-12 p-lg-5 mx-auto my-5">
				<h1 class="display-3 fw-bold">Blood Connect</h1>
				<h3 class="siteDescription text-light"><br />
					Blood Connect is a platform that enables the connection between blood donors and blood banks.<br />
					Donors and blood banks require swift solutions and reliability. <br />
					Count on us.
				</h3><br />
				<div class="d-flex gap-3 justify-content-center lead fw-normal">
					<a class="btn btn-secondary btn-md" asp-area="" asp-controller="About" asp-action="Index" role="button">More about us &raquo;</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="container py-4">
			<div class="row align-items-md-stretch">
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="h-100 p-5 text-bg-dark rounded-3">
						<h2>Donor</h2>
						<p>If you are a donor candidate seeking to contribute, please register with us.</p>
						<a class="btn btn-outline-light" asp-area="" asp-controller="Donor" asp-action="Create" role="button">Register</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="h-100 p-5 bg-body-tertiary border rounded-3">
						<h2>Blood Bank</h2>
						<p>
							If you represent a blood bank and wish to become our partner, please contact us, and we will
							promptly respond to your inquiry.
						</p>
						<a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" asp-area="" asp-controller="Contact" asp-action="Create" role="button">Get in touch</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<br />

			<div class="homeDonationInfo position-relative overflow-hidden p-3 p-md-5 m-md-3 text-center">
			<div class="container py-3">
				<div class="text-center">
					<h2 class="section-heading">Why donate blood?</h2><br />
					<h4 class="fw-normal text-muted mb-3 fs-5">
						Blood donation is a voluntary and altruistic act of extreme importance, as human blood cannot be artificially
						manufactured. Therefore, the only way to save the lives of patients who need blood transfusion is through this
						gesture of love and solidarity. <br /><br />
						Learn everything about the donation process. You'll see that it's simple, quick and safe.
					</h4>
				</div>
				<br />
